{% set e = establishment() %}
<div id="contact" class="hours">
    <h2 class="hours__title">Horaires d’ouverture · {{ e.name }} · Gorges</h2>
    {% for row in weekly_hours() %}
        <div class="hours__row">
            <span class="hours__day">{{ row.day }}{{ row.today ? ' (aujourd’hui)' : '' }}</span>
            <span class="hours__val">{{ row.hours }}</span>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}
    <div class="note note--tight">
        <svg class="ico--t1" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#b3743f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 8v5M12 16h.01"></path></svg>
        <p>Nous proposons les <strong>grandes pizzas à la demande</strong>, de 11h30 à 14h00 et de 18h00 jusqu’à la fermeture.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hours__coords">
        <div class="coord coord--top"><svg class="ico--t2" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#a59b88" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg><span>{{ e.address }}</span></div>
        <div class="coord"><svg class="ico" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#a59b88" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.9.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg><a href="tel:{{ e.phoneHref }}">{{ e.phone }}</a></div>
        <div class="coord"><svg class="ico" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#a59b88" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect><path d="m22 7-10 6L2 7"></path></svg><a href="mailto:{{ e.email }}">{{ e.email }}</a></div>
    </div>
</div>
